515
00:29:15,100 --> 00:29:16,124
Help them.

516
00:29:17,169 --> 00:29:19,399
No, you're not.

517
00:29:22,775 --> 00:29:25,676
-You Randall Thompson?
-How'd you.... Where's my assistant?

518
00:29:25,744 --> 00:29:28,611
-Sit down. This will only take a second.
