519
00:29:28,681 --> 00:29:30,046
Harrison Davies.

520
00:29:30,149 --> 00:29:32,083
RANDALL: Lindsay's Harrison.
HARRlSON: Right.

521
00:29:32,151 --> 00:29:34,847
